snippet.title: Best VGM 1762 - Mega Man Soccer - Wood Man
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Mega Man Soccer (1994)
Wood Man
Toshio Okamoto, Norihiko Togashi & Kenichi Tomizawa
